Gujarat
Sep 26, 2014
Domestic Violence, Dowry Harassment
Description:
			A 28-year-old man and his family members were booked for allegedly harassing his wife and demanding Rs 5.5 lakh dowry.

Supriya Belani, 31, a resident of Adajan lodged a complaint against her husband Ashish Belani, father-in-law Sushil, mother-in-law Lata and brother-in-law Akash. Supriya said in her compliant that she was being physically and mentally harassed for dowry ever since the marriage in 2010. Police are investigating the case and the accused will be called to register their statements.